295
00:20:17,350 --> 00:20:18,830
Ang Helian Tribe ay mahina,

296
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:20,820
at walang silbi si Helian Chuan.

297
00:20:21,260 --> 00:20:23,550
Kung hindi ko ginawang konsorte si Helian Ling,

298
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,240
pastulan ng kanilang tribo

299
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:29,210
kinulit na sana
ng ibang mga tribo noon pa man.

300
00:20:53,510 --> 00:20:54,030
Magsalita.

301
00:20:54,930 --> 00:20:56,260
Anong gusto mong gawin ko?

302
00:20:57,260 --> 00:20:59,120
Ano ang ibig mong sabihin, Consort Helian?

303
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:02,080
Kahapon, alam mo
Nasa labas ako ng tent,

304
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:05,000
