329
00:24:43,310 --> 00:24:44,630
tulungan mo siya?

330
00:24:49,550 --> 00:24:51,270
Ay hindi, ito ay isang bitag!

331
00:25:01,330 --> 00:25:01,890
Retreat!

332
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:04,720
Retreat!

333
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:10,160
Young Master,

334
00:25:10,290 --> 00:25:11,280
Aakayin ko ang ilang lalaki para gambalain sila.

335
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:12,080
Sige, go.

336
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:16,960
Tumigil ka!

337
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:18,670
Sa ganitong paraan!

338
00:25:21,810 --> 00:25:22,470
Pagkatapos nila!

339
00:25:23,130 --> 00:25:23,650
Magmadali!

340
00:25:28,730 --> 00:25:29,830
Ito ay isang talampas dito.

341
00:25:29,830 --> 00:25:31,460
Bumagsak kana,
at ikaw ay patay o baldado.

342
00:25:31,460 --> 00:25:32,220
Tara na!

343
00:25:32,700 --> 00:25:33,500
Go!

344
00:25:43,790 --> 00:25:46,070
Nagkaroon kami ng stalemate
kasama ang hukbong Biantang sa loob ng ilang araw,

345
00:25:46,070 --> 00:25:48,160
at sila ay nasa likod ng kanilang mga pader.

346
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:48,750
Ngayon,

347
00:25:49,270 --> 00:25:51,400
Heneral Chu Qiao ng Xiuli Army ni Biantang

348
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:52,800
ay nasa aking kampo sa Great Yan,

349
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:55,980
at ang pangunahing puwersa ng Xiuli Army
ay tinambangan ngayon.

350
00:25:57,030 --> 00:25:58,830
Ang Longyin Pass ay wala nang pinuno.

351
00:25:59,310 --> 00:26:00,640
Aalis tayo mamayang gabi,

352
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:02,360
pindutin ang aming kalamangan,

353
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:04,130
at kumuha ng Longyin Pass sa isang iglap!

354
00:26:04,130 --> 00:26:05,760
Oo, Kamahalan!

355
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:33,920
Tumigil ka!

356
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:37,760
Kamahalan,

357
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:38,790
