na pinakilos natin.

363
00:26:46,110 --> 00:26:46,790
Nag-aalala lang ako...

364
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:47,480
Ipasa ang aking mga order—

365
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:49,480
ang buong hukbo ay mabilis na sumulong
sa pamamagitan ng lambak

366
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,550
at direktang hinampas ang pass!

367
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:51,350
Kamahalan.

368
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:53,480
Marso!

369
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:54,030
Magmadali!

370
00:27:06,140 --> 00:27:06,940
Kamahalan,

371
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,250
