374
00:27:17,940 --> 00:27:18,440
Sunog!

375
00:28:08,540 --> 00:28:09,980
Zhuge Yue.

376
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:12,020
Ang liham na ito ay peke.

377
00:28:12,790 --> 00:28:15,330
Wala itong sikretong code
ng Qingshan Manor dito.

378
00:28:15,330 --> 00:28:18,000
Ang parol na ito ay nanggaling sa direksyon
ng kampo militar ng Great Yan.

379
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:18,880
Tanging si General Chu

380
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,590
alam ang aming paraan ng pagmemensahe
sa Qingshan Manor.

381
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:21,240
Kung gayon bakit siya

382
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:22,790
padalhan kami ng maling mensahe?

383
00:28:23,030 --> 00:28:23,830
Abisuhan si Lin Mu

384
00:28:24,080 --> 00:28:25,680
para tipunin ang mga elite ng Xiuli Army

385
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:27,160
at umalis kaagad ngayong gabi.

386
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:27,720
Oo, sir.

387
00:28:28,360 --> 00:28:28,950
Teka.

388
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:30,780
At sabihin kay He Xiao

389
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:32,090
upang itakda kaagad

390
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,640
hanggang 50 li sa labas ng Longyin Pass

391
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,640
upang matugunan ang mga reinforcement ni Zhao Che.

392
00:29:42,440 --> 00:29:43,170
Heneral Chu?

393
00:29:47,750 --> 00:29:48,480
Heneral Chu?

394
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:55,240
Heneral Chu?

395
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:56,610
Isang tao, halika!

396
00:29:58,540 --> 00:30:00,240
-Kamahalan.
-Kamahalan!

397
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:01,240
Buksan ang pinto.

398
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,240
Buksan mo ang pinto!

399
00:30:14,830 --> 00:30:15,880
Mag-ingat ka.

400
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,960
Mahuli siya! Huwag hayaan siyang makatakas!

401
00:30:28,330 --> 00:30:29,200
Mahuli siya!

402
00:30:34,570 --> 00:30:35,770
Huwag hayaan siyang makatakas!

403
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:52,960
Tumigil ka!

404
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:14,310
Tulong! Sunog!

405
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:25,710
Magmadali! Ituloy ang paghabol!

406
00:31:26,270 --> 00:31:27,760
Bumalik ka at patayin ang apoy!

407
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:29,020
Nasusunog ang kamalig!

408
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:30,070
Kumuha ng tubig!

409
00:31:30,470 --> 00:31:30,990
Mabilis!

410
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:21,120
Kamahalan.

411
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:05,000
♪ Nahuhulog ang mga bulaklak sa manggas ♪

412
00:33:05,110 --> 00:33:07,660
♪ Hindi nila naiintindihan ang kalungkutan ko ♪

413
00:33:08,090 --> 00:33:09,390
♪ Sa isang palayok ng alak ♪

414
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:10,880
♪ Lumalakas ang pananabik ko ♪

415
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:13,410
♪ Nagiging haggard ako ♪

416
00:33:14,020 --> 00:33:16,460
♪ Pumapatak ang malambot na ulan sa bintana ♪

417
00:33:16,510 --> 00:33:19,330
♪ Paggising mula sa panaginip,
Hindi ko na alam kung anong taon na ♪

418
00:33:19,350 --> 00:33:21,050
♪ Ang aking pag-ibig ay nananatili ♪

419
00:33:21,360 --> 00:33:24,730
♪ Pero wala ka na ♪

420
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:27,030
♪ Ang hinahanap ko sa buhay ♪

421
00:33:27,050 --> 00:33:28,640
♪ Wala na
kaysa lumingon muli ♪

422
00:33:28,660 --> 00:33:31,250
♪ Sa halimuyak pa rin ♪

423
00:33:31,270 --> 00:33:32,860
♪ Sa nanginginig na mga kamay na ito ♪

424
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:36,070
♪ Nananatili pa rin ang pananabik ko ♪

425
00:33:36,090 --> 00:33:38,450
♪ Mga salitang hindi binibigkas ♪

426
00:33:38,030 --> 00:33:38,750
Zhuge Yue,

427
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,990
♪ Nauwi sa guilt ♪

428
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:40,400
