443
00:34:05,130 --> 00:34:08,010
♪ Ang hindi kayang itago,
mapapaalis lang ♪

444
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:08,480
Hinding hindi tayo magiging tunay
tumayo sa magkasalungat na panig.

445
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:11,300
♪ Sa huli ♪

446
00:34:41,250 --> 00:34:42,050
Kamahalan,

447
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:43,179
